---
title: Spicy Spaghetti Amatriciana with Bacon plus Parmesan & Chili Flakes
description: Al dente pasta, smoky bacon, luscious tomatoes, spicy chili flakes, and savory Parmesan cheese—these are the simple ingredients that come together quickly in a hot pan to become a beloved dish Italians have enjoyed for centuries: spaghetti amatriciana. Bring a taste of Italy to your kitchen, and make it tonight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/664cb0096dac4f56a86a0391-f66ed11e.jpeg
